This paper deals with access control policies, which is a topic in computer security (cs.CR). The paper also presents a new algorithm for mining policies from timed ACLs, which involves data mining techniques (cs.DB). The algorithm uses multiple quality metrics, including interpretability, which is a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the complexity of the policies and how to optimize it, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and software engineering (cs.SE).
